Jfr Analysis to Identify the Bottlenecks of the application and pefromance related issues... more over identify the exact place issue occurs and problemetic lines of code which causing the issues.
Steps are like collecting the access log for the High Response time API Transactions.
Collect the application logs for the respective high response time transaction and identify on which process its spent more time in overall time.
Then open tehe collected JFRs in JDK Mission Controller application to check thread which we find in the access log for the high response time transaction.
Sort the thread and check the stack trace for the issue in Event browser.
